query:
UPDATE island_guides 
SET nearbyAirports = JSON_ARRAY(
  JSON_OBJECT(
    'name', 'Malé International Airport',
    'code', 'MLE',
    'transferType', 'Speedboat',
    'duration', '1-2 hours',
    'distance', '50-100 km',
    'description', COALESCE(flightInfo, speedboatInfo, ferryInfo, CONCAT('International flights to Malé, then speedboat to ', name))
  )
)
WHERE nearbyAirports IS NULL OR JSON_LENGTH(nearbyAirports) = 0;
